Albie.

77
00:06:22,821 --> 00:06:25,237
Hello. How you doing?

78
00:06:25,261 --> 00:06:26,997
Just hand it over.

79
00:06:27,021 --> 00:06:28,997
Please.

80
00:06:29,021 --> 00:06:32,317
Sorry, I'm stressed. Yeah,
well, doing a job on bail

81
