246
00:19:36,021 --> 00:19:37,661
Good idea.

247
00:19:43,501 --> 00:19:46,181
Just the one sugar, Kirsty.

248
00:20:05,821 --> 00:20:07,437
Can I bring you one, Joan?

249
00:20:07,461 --> 00:20:08,901
No, thanks.

250
00:20:24,981 --> 00:20:28,101
Well done.

251
00:20:39,221 --> 00:20:41,501
